# OS/2 version

# Setup colorsets
Read $./Colorsets

DestroyDecor recreate WindowDecoration
AddToDecor WindowDecoration

+ TitleStyle Inactive TiledPixmap $./title-inactive.png
+ TitleStyle Active TiledPixmap $./title-active.png
+ TitleStyle Centered
+ TitleStyle -- flat
+ TitleStyle Height 20

+ BorderStyle -- HiddenHandles
+ BorderStyle -- Flat

# Close
+ ButtonStyle 1 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray-red.png
+ ButtonStyle 1 Active Pixmap $./button-red-icon.png

# Maximize
+ ButtonStyle 2 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray-green.png
+ ButtonStyle 2 Active Pixmap $./button-green-icon.png

# Iconify
+ ButtonStyle 4 Inactive Pixmap $./button-gray-yellow.png
+ ButtonStyle 4 Active Pixmap $./button-yellow-icon.png

+ ButtonStyle All -- UseTitleStyle
+ ButtonStyle All -- flat

Style * HandleWidth 1, BorderWidth 1
Style * Colorset                $[cs-window-inactive], \
        BorderColorset          $[cs-window-inactive], \
        HilightColorset         $[cs-window-active], \
        HilightBorderColorset   $[cs-window-active]

Style * Font "xft:Arial:pixelsize=15"

Style * UseDecor WindowDecoration

# Setup button functions
Include components/decorations/Buttons-os2

